node.title: Police seek fourth person allegedly involved in west Auckland murder
node.content: ["A fourth person is being sought by police for murder after a shooting in west Auckland.", "Three people were charged with murder on Wednesday after 40-year-old James Robert Hart was\u00a0\u00a0\"senselessly killed in a driveway\" on New Lynn's Great North Rd on Friday morning, police said.", "On Thursday, Det Insp Kevin\u00a0McNaughton said the investigation team want the public's help to find 35-year-old Dylan James Mitchell Harris, who has a warrant for his arrest.", "McNaughton said Harris has singnificant gang connections across the North Island.", "Harris is considered dangerous and shouldn't be approached,\u00a0McNaughton said.", "\u00a0"]
